results.description:
This is a captive bred lion that goes on lion walks and night encounters where they get to hunt zebras and wildebeest to allow for them to retain their hunting instincts.

It is these lions that are released into fenced, managed and secure semi-wild environment, where they will live as a wild pride, without any form of human interaction. 

Their offspring will then be released into the wild.
